- Oh, not if it was sawn-off.

01:41:11.286 --> 01:41:14.286
They can make them pretty small.
Catherine, love, you can't park there.

01:41:14.366 --> 01:41:16.566
Leave that clear.
We've got the SOCO coming down.

01:41:18.366 --> 01:41:20.606
Did you like the musical last night?

01:41:21.326 --> 01:41:25.246
Yeah, I did. It was good fun.
Pretty music.

01:41:25.326 --> 01:41:27.726
Yeah, he's very good.

01:41:28.366 --> 01:41:30.486
I'm gonna get tickets
for Mummy and Papa.

01:41:30.566 --> 01:41:32.606
Good.

