01:41:53.726 --> 01:41:55.526
Jesus Christ!

01:41:59.486 --> 01:42:01.526
Apparently, she was
coming home from work,

01:42:01.606 --> 01:42:05.566
and someone who was already there
who'd burgled another flat and rob...

01:42:05.646 --> 01:42:08.166
And shot an old lady,
ran into Nola by chance, and...

01:42:08.246 --> 01:42:12.206
She was entering the building,
and he was running out and he shot her.

01:42:12.286 --> 01:42:14.566
Oh, my God.

01:42:20.126 --> 01:42:21.646
Hello?

