01:42:36.286 --> 01:42:37.966
I know.

01:42:38.006 --> 01:42:40.566
Wait, wait, that must be him.
I'll call you back.

01:42:40.646 --> 01:42:42.406
Hello?

01:42:42.446 --> 01:42:44.966
Yeah, we've just read it,
and Mummy just called.

01:42:45.046 --> 01:42:47.886
Well, yeah, yeah, I know.
I mean, wrong place at the wrong time.

01:42:47.966 --> 01:42:49.326
I suppose she must've...

01:42:49.406 --> 01:42:52.046
I mean, disturbed a burglar
or burglars, or whatever.

01:42:52.126 --> 01:42:54.406
