how many of them there were.

01:42:54.486 --> 01:42:56.206
Well, even Mummy's really shaken up,

01:42:56.286 --> 01:42:58.486
and you know they
weren't exactly friends.

01:42:58.526 --> 01:43:01.806
It says here that there's been a rise
in drug-related crime in the area

01:43:01.886 --> 01:43:03.766
over the past year.

01:43:03.846 --> 01:43:06.486
Did you hear that? Yeah.

01:43:06.566 --> 01:43:10.926
I just can't believe it.
It's just... I know.

01:43:17.246 --> 01:43:18.646
Mummy.

01:43:20.806 --> 01:43:22.806
I've got something to tell you.

01:43:22.886 --> 01:43:24.886
