01:43:26.206 --> 01:43:28.086
Chris?

01:43:28.126 --> 01:43:31.126
- Where'd he go?
- I don't know.

01:43:31.206 --> 01:43:33.206
He was just in here. Chris?

01:43:33.886 --> 01:43:35.886
Chris?

01:43:43.206 --> 01:43:44.566
He was just here.

01:43:44.606 --> 01:43:46.286
Well, what did you want to tell me?

01:43:46.366 --> 01:43:48.806
Just wait. Wait, wait. Chris?

01:44:21.166 --> 01:44:23.326
Where are you? Chris?

01:44:24.846 --> 01:44:26.086
Well, what did you want to tell me?

01:44:26.166 --> 01:44:27.846
Well, I just really want him to be here.

01:44:27.926 --> 01:44:30.246
Hang on, there he is. There you are!

01:44:30.806 --> 01:44:32.926
- Can we tell her now?
- Sure.

01:44:33.006 --> 01:44:35.246
Well, I wanted you to be here.

01:44:35.326 --> 01:44:36.846
Well, what is it?

01:44:36.926 --> 01:44:38.406
Mummy...

01:44:38.486 --> 01:44:41.246
You can finally
crack open the champagne.

01:44:41.326 --> 01:44:43.046
It looks like I'm pregnant.

01:44:43.126 --> 01:44:45.366
- When did you hear?
- This morning.

01:44:45.446 --> 01:44:49.246
- Oh, I'm so delighted.
- Oh, good.

01:44:49.886 --> 01:44:51.366
Alec?

01:44:51.446 --> 01:44:54.166
Alec? Come here.

01:44:54.366 --> 01:44:56.806
We're both walking on air.

01:44:56.846 --> 01:45:00.006
Well, you're walking on air. Your
husband looks a bit shell shocked.

01:45:00.086 --> 01:45:01.966
- 'Cause I've exhausted him, poor thing.
- What?

01:45:02.046 --> 01:45:03.286
Chloe's pregnant.

01:45:03.366 --> 01:45:05.846
Oh, what a great day.
Oh, my darling, congratulations.

01:45:05.886 --> 01:45:08.286
I'm absolutely thrilled.
I couldn't be more pleased.

01:45:08.366 --> 01:45:10.006
Thank you so much.
It's such a relief.

01:45:10.086 --> 01:45:11.046
Excuse me, sir. Excuse me.

01:45:11.126 --> 01:45:12.686
- Yes?
- Phone call, sir. Your secretary.

01:45:12.726 --> 01:45:15.126
It's wonderful, isn't it? Look at her,
doesn't she look gorgeous?

01:45:15.166 --> 01:45:18.966
- Margaret, I'm pregnant!
- Congratulations! That's wonderful.

01:45:19.046 --> 01:45:20.486
Thank you, Margaret.

01:45:21.406 --> 01:45:22.886
Sam?

01:45:22.966 --> 01:45:25.526
Yeah, there's a message for you
that a Mike Banner,

01:45:25.606 --> 01:45:27.486
Detective Mike Banner, called.

01:45:27.566 --> 01:45:30.686
He wants you to call him
at Shepherd's Bush police station.

01:45:31.166 --> 01:45:34.206
Yeah. No, I don't think it's urgent,
but he left a number.

01:45:34.326 --> 01:45:36.246
- Banner?
- Sweetheart...

01:45:36.286 --> 01:45:37.686
I bet it was that night...

01:45:37.766 --> 01:45:41.046
- You better give me the number.
- Look, that's flattering.

01:45:43.526 --> 01:45:47.006
Well, the last time you went,
he said everything was fine, didn't he?

01:45:47.086 --> 01:45:49.246
Yes, and he just made me
completely calm down.

01:45:49.326 --> 01:45:51.526
Oh, I just can't believe it.
It's marvelous.

01:45:51.566 --> 01:45:53.166
OK. Thanks, Samantha. Bye.

01:45:53.246 --> 01:45:55.806
He just seemed odd,
there was something weird.

01:45:57.926 --> 01:46:01.126
- Granny would have been thrilled.
...alternative medicine.

01:46:01.206 --> 01:46:04.366
Granny would have loved it.
I wish she could be here.

01:46:04.446 --> 01:46:07.246
- Thank God. Thank God.
- Congratulations!

01:46:07.326 --> 01:46:09.086
Detective Banner, please.

01:46:09.166 --> 01:46:11.166
This is Chris Wilton.

01:46:14.846 --> 01:46:15.846
Oh, hello.

01:46:15.926 --> 01:46:18.406
This is Chris Wilton. You called?

01:46:18.526 --> 01:46:21.366
Oh, yes. I was wondering if there
was a time you could drop in here?

01:46:21.446 --> 01:46:23.686
Or if it's more convenient,
we can come and see you.

01:46:23.766 --> 01:46:27.166
- In reference to what?
- I'd rather not explain on the phone.

01:46:27.246 --> 01:46:30.526
It's just a few questions, and I'm sure
you'd prefer it to be discreet.

01:46:33.406 --> 01:46:35.606
I've no reason to bring a lawyer, do I?

01:46:35.686 --> 01:46:37.686
I certainly hope not.

01:47:44.246 --> 01:47:46.806
- Chris Wilton. Detective Banner.
- Good afternoon.

01:47:46.886 --> 01:47:49.886
- How do you do? Take a seat.
- Thank you.

01:47:50.806 --> 01:47:52.806
This is nothing to be alarmed about.

01:47:52.886 --> 01:47:56.926
We're just doing a routine investigation
into the Betty Eastby-Nola Rice murders.

01:47:58.526 --> 01:48:01.246
Were you acquainted
with either of the victims?

01:48:01.326 --> 01:48:03.686
Peripherally, I knew Nola Rice.

01:48:04.286 --> 01:48:05.526
How?

01:48:06.446 --> 01:48:09.726
