to the man who's now my brother-in-law.

01:48:09.806 --> 01:48:11.526
That's...

01:48:12.206 --> 01:48:14.326
...Tom Hewett?
- That's correct.

01:48:16.166 --> 01:48:19.406
They broke up. A year ago. More.

01:48:20.846 --> 01:48:22.846
When did you last see her?

01:48:23.766 --> 01:48:26.086
Oh, God, I can't remember.

01:48:29.526 --> 01:48:32.766
At the Tate Modern.
My wife and I ran into her.

01:48:32.846 --> 01:48:35.286
But that was a long time ago.

01:48:37.126 --> 01:48:38.766
Have you seen her since?

01:48:39.166 --> 01:48:40.966
Not that I recall.

01:48:43.726 --> 01:48:45.366
Have?

01:48:46.566 --> 01:48:48.006
Have you ever seen this?

01:48:49.006 --> 01:48:50.966
No. What is it?

01:48:52.286 --> 01:48:54.886
Are you aware
that Nola Rice kept a diary?

01:49:04.406 --> 01:49:06.086
No.

01:49:07.086 --> 01:49:09.086
As you can see...

01:49:09.686 --> 01:49:12.086
...you're all over it.

01:49:19.326 --> 01:49:21.686
Yes, I can see that.

01:49:24.926 --> 01:49:27.126
Do you still claim
that you haven't seen her,

01:49:27.206 --> 01:49:29.726
except for more than a year ago
at the Tate Modern?

01:49:32.766 --> 01:49:36.326
You can't blame me for trying to hide
the fact that I had an affair with her.

01:49:36.966 --> 01:49:39.326
