to leave your wife and marry Miss Rice?

01:50:18.366 --> 01:50:20.446
No, I did not.

01:50:20.806 --> 01:50:23.166
I mean, it's possible
she had that fantasy.

01:50:24.126 --> 01:50:27.406
And, obviously, she wrote that I did.

01:50:32.846 --> 01:50:35.566
But I tried to finesse
that point with her.

01:50:35.646 --> 01:50:37.886
I didn't want the
sexual relationship to end,

01:50:37.966 --> 01:50:40.046
but I'm not gonna break up my home.

01:50:41.766 --> 01:50:44.726
My wife and I are
trying very hard to have a baby.

01:50:44.766 --> 01:50:48.446
We've seen several
fertility doctors, et cetera.

01:50:49.526 --> 01:50:53.126
